  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dc4\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0d82 \u0dbb\u0dda\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three and a half million worth of gold brought from Paris gets stuck in customs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Sudatta Silva, Director of Customs, said that the customs officers of the airport seized a consignment of gold worth more than three and a half million rupees, which was illegally brought by a Sri Lankan passenger who arrived early today (27) on a flight belonging to SriLankan Airlines from Paris.",
        "The customs spokesman said that they tried to carry 2414.6 grams of gold on the green route for passengers who had nothing to declare to the customs, hidden very carefully in the luggage, pretending to be personal belongings and the amount of gold seized was estimated at 36,219,000 rupees.",
        "Mr. Sudatta Silva further mentioned that the Customs will conduct further investigations regarding this stock of gold, confiscate the stock of gold and impose fines on the airport duty officers of Sri Lanka Customs."
      ],
